C     UPDATED  VERSION--APRIL     2002. PRINT OUT ORDER OF METHODS ON
C                                       PLOT
C     UPDATED  VERSION--OCTOBER   2002. ADD ICAPSW, ICAPTY TO CALL
C                                       LIST (PASS TO DPMAN2)
C     UPDATED  VERSION--MAY       2010. UPDATE LIST OF METHODS
