C     UPDATED         --FEBRUARY  2009. ONE SAMPLE T TEST
C                                       ONE SAMPLE T TEST CDF
C     UPDATED         --FEBRUARY  2009. CHI-SQUARE SD TEST
C                                       CHI-SQUARE SD TEST CDF
C     UPDATED         --FEBRUARY  2009. FREQUENCY TEST
